like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-05T06:42:08.000Z","msg":"包括 Macrumors、9to5Mac 在內多個美國科技網站收到聲稱是蘋果授權維修商的內部文件，說蘋果得知部分 iPhone 7 和 iPhone 7 Plus 用戶在升級 iOS 11.3 之後收音咪失靈，無法在通話時使用「擴音」功能甚至令收音咪無法運作。蘋果要求授權維修商在維修客戶 iPhone 前先要求客人移除連接耳機或其他音響裝置，去檢查 iPhone 的收音咪是否能正常操作。<br />\n<br />\n在檢查期間如果發現利用 iPhone 通話無法擴音或收音咪失靈，授權維修商就要為 iPhone 進行音效診斷，如果發現「裝置不能連接」或者「元件並不支援」的情況，授權維修商就會維修 iPhone。如果受收音咪問題影響的 iPhone 7 和 iPhone 7 Plus 過保，授權維修商可以向蘋果發出豁免要求，雖然蘋果文件沒有提及免費，但似乎可以讓授權維修商酌情處理，包括免費更換 iPhone。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.newmobilelife.com/2018/05/05/iphone-7-ios-11-3-microphone-bug/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.newmobilelife.com%2F2018%2F05%2F05%2Fiphone-7-ios-11-3-microphone-bug%2F&d=FEX5tlkpPGC2vXGalhBCLC7PofNJLCAwyGXsi6MH%2FEQ%3D&h=d94c36c2\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.newmobilelife.com/2018/05/05/iphone-7-ios-11-3-microphone-bug/</a>"},{"pid":"ab5fff15b49ca1e94839d80fa55de33c0b6ac797","tid":653890,"uid":19454,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"6e512694b876d7854a3379d3e0e5ca04435f03ba","tid":653890,"uid":115849,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-05T06:41:55.000Z","msg":"咁你咪好叻？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-05T06:42:31.000Z","msg":"係Gay cook廢"},{"pid":"d987f44bcb23a5e67d8825c9f2b3642b2233e2ec","tid":653890,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-05T06:44:08.000Z","msg":"唔怪得我trade in時，完全冇測試收音mic<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3c591b74c9e84633fc97bc61d340ed131bf44e14","tid":653890,"uid":109983,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-05T06:45:45.000Z","msg":"我依加仲係ios10.1.1<br />\n11太柒 control centre太亂<br />\nWhatsapp又變到好柒大大隻字'對話'係度 <br />\n完全唔想升<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3ca08a2c3a2a2585fac753b906efc659b8725825","tid":653890,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"cite